query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(mk mi_idx) NoMergeJoin(mi_idx mk cc) NoHashJoin(cc k mi_idx mk cct2) NoMergeJoin(cc cct2 k mi_idx mk t) NoHashJoin(cc cct2 k mi_idx mk t kt) NoHashJoin(cc cct2 k kt mi_idx mk t ci) NoHashJoin(cc cct2 ci k kt mi_idx mk t n) NoNestLoop(cc cct2 ci k kt mi_idx mk n t cct1) NoMergeJoin(cc cct1 cct2 ci k kt mi_idx mk n t chn) NoNestLoop(cc cct1 cct2 chn ci k kt mi_idx mk n t it2) */ select min(chn.name) AS character_name,
min(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
min(n.name) AS playing_actor,
min(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
from movie_keyword AS mk
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info > '7.0'
inner join complete_cast AS cc
on cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
inner join keyword AS k
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('based-on-novel',
'murder',
'gore',
'tv-special',
'tv-special',
'based-on-novel',
'claw',
'laser',
'martial-arts',
'gore')
inner join comp_cast_type AS cct2
on cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind like '%complete%'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year > 1996
inner join kind_type AS kt
on kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'movie'
inner join cast_info AS ci
on ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
inner join name AS n
on n.id = ci.person_id
inner join comp_cast_type AS cct1
on cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast'
inner join char_name AS chn
on chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND chn.name IS NOT NULL AND ( chn.name like '%man%' OR chn.name like '%Man%')
inner join info_type AS it2
on it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating';
